The paper discusses a novel approach to deep reinforcement learning, which involves meta-learning and recurrent networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the potential implications for robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY), which further support these categories.
